channel.title: Dupe Free!
channel.description:
Hey Guys, I was Wondering If There Was A Tut For Devolution Server 7.0 Or Someone Could Tell Me How To Stop Any And All Interfaces Coming Up While Dueling To Stop Duping, By Interfaces I Mean Make It Impossible To Open ::Players And Click Report Abuse Whilst In A Duel So Im Pretty Much Asking For Help On How To Stop Any Sort Of Screen Coming Up Whilst Dueling. I Know This Is Possible Because Delta Has Infmormed Me It Is Possible And Kiwon (Owner Of kiwiiscape.no-ip.org) Has Managed To Do It. Any And All Help Would Be Appreciated Guys.
I Know Theres Fellow Members Out There Wondering Why Can't He Work Out Himself....Simple.....Im An Amateur And Have No Experience In This Side Of Client.Java And Besides We All Remember When You Were Noobs Like Me. I've Also Searched Frequently For Some Sort Of Tut And Have Come To This Conclusion As A Last Resort As I Do Not Like Other Members And Players Taking Time Out Of Their Activities To Help People Like Me Out. :D
All Help Is Welcome And Appreciated.

return;
}

I don’t know what the variable dodian has for it, but that’s what you should do for it.
